n><hr size=1> I have the strangest luck.  I'm one of those people that starts a new character every couple months.  I get bored for awhile with one, start another.  Well, every time I start a new one, no matter what zone I'm in, someone will give me something.  I'm just sitting there, waiting for my lvl 2's health to come back up or whatever, and someone will (usually without saying a word) give me a piece of pretty nice or even awesome equipment.  I don't usually twink my new characters as none of them have anything special.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   And it always makes me really happy when someone is nice enough to do this.  Ditto on buffs, etc.  They can mean a lot to a level 2.<br>
