<br>
I do not hang in EC all day. I am out hunting and using the stuff I strip off of kills. I don't have the time or inclination to participate in the E Marr economy. I come on to explore, fight, and have fun, then I log off.<br>
<br>
When I loot something I don't need, it goes right to the nearest merchant. I really can't be bothered to sit and spam a chat channel, there's better things to be done.<br>
<br>
Not whining or ranting, but a true Noob, will not have 500 pp in their pocket to invest in such a ludicrous waste of time.<br>
